         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(Recto);;[- - -] but also I have nothing to wear and we are living in the open. Will you kindly then order them to give me 4 drachmai, that I may buy at least an old cloak [- - -];;(Verso);;Petosiris</ab>
         </div>
